content: Install Privacy Pass addon in Google Chrome or Firefox browser.Google Chrome - https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/privacy-pass/ajhmfdgkijocedmfjonnpjfojldioehi.Firefox - https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/privacy-pass/. Additional info - https://privacypass.github.io.Then go here https://captcha.website/ and tick the box and verify that you are human, each tick will give you ~30 Cloudflare passes. You will need ~200 Cloudfare passes.Now when you will go to the site with Cloudflare protection, you will not have any problem.
